=============================
=  README for ex4:   =
=============================


==================
=  Description:  =
==================
'update_word_pattern' - this function check if the letter is in the word,
and update the pattern of the letter is in the word.

'run_single_game' - this function use some of the function from the
hangman_helper.py and start the game.

'filter_words_list' - if the user ask for hint, this function return to him
a letter. this function filter the word list by same length to the pattern
and filter the list if the letter from the pattern are not or not in the
exactly place in the words.

'choose_letter' - at the end the function return the most occurrence
word in the list.

======================
=  Special Comments  =
======================
answer:
First we need to change the 'word list' to word in hebrew, fro get a random
hebrew word. second we need to change some small thing in the function.
like in the function 'choose_letter' - we need to change the alphabet list
to 22 letters(to check for all the letters in hebrew).